title: 2012 NERF LIVE FROM THE CIGAR BAR!
itunes:title: 2012 NERF LIVE FROM THE CIGAR BAR!
description: Live from The Cigar Bar in Worcester, MA for this year's big NERF! What is NERF? Tune in and find out! On today's show we're smoking the mysterious 'ESY Unknown' and the newest cigar from La Mezcla Cubana. Later in the show Dave and Mr Jonathan interview local broadcast legend, Jack Williams. An instant classic you don't want to miss!
